## Introduction

![Laravel Mix thumbnail](https://repository-images.githubusercontent.com/76991633/43a4fe80-025e-11eb-8b88-bf742e4412a7)


Laravel SnowMix provides a clean, fluent API for defining basic [Snowpack](http://github.com/snowpackjs/snowpack) build steps for your applications. SnowMix supports several common CSS and JavaScript pre-processors.

If you've ever been confused about how to get started with module bundling and asset compilation, you will love Laravel SnowMix!

## Documentation

You may review the initial documentation [here](docs/).

